          <td>37.5 MB/s</td>
          <td>30-35 MB/s</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>1 Gbps</td>
          <td>125 MB/s</td>
          <td>100-115 MB/s</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <div class="info-box">
        <h4>快速換算</h4>
        <p>Mbps ÷ 10 ≈ 實際下載速度（MB/s）</p>
      </div>
    </section>
